import React,{useState,useEffect} from 'react'; import {FaS} from 'react-icons/fa' import axios from 'axios' function GroupOfCountries({darkMode}) { const [countries,setCountry]=useState([]); useEffect(()=>{ axios.get("https://restcountries.com/v2/all") .then(res=>{ console.log(res) setCountry(res.data) }) .catch(error=>console.log(error)); }) return ( <>
{countries.map((country)=> (

{country.name}

Population:{""} {country.population}

Regions:{""} {country.region}

Capital:{""} {country.capital}

) )}
) } export default GroupOfCountries
